10-常见几何体
  BoxGeometry(长,宽,高,widthSegment,heightSegment,depthSegment)
  CircleGeometry(半径,几个,起始角度,结束角度)
  ConeGeometry(半径,高度,radiusSegment,heightSegment,是否底边,起始角度,结束角度)
  CylinderGeometry(上,下,高,几个,几个,是否底边,起始角度,结束角度)
  DodecahedronGeometry
  EdgesGeometry
  PlaneGeometry
  RingGeometry
  SphereGeometry

